{"title":"用rEFInd-theme-Yours解决FydeOS UEFI安全启动问题 ","date":"2025-07-26T12:33:41.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2025年7月26日","L":"2025/07/26","MM-DD":"07-26"},"link":"2025/07/26/2025-07-26-fydeos-uefi","tags":["Operating Systems"],"updated":"2025-09-13T07:01:02.439Z","content":"<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n  <li>\n    能够访问Github\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    DiskGenius\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    BIOS支持64位UEFI（若不支持可参考下载链接中的教程）\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>1.下载</strong><br>\n必须：<a href=\"https://github.com/M-L-P/grub2-fyde\" target=\"_blank\">Grub2 Fyde 2</a></p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n  <li>\n    BIOS支持64位UEFI：<a href=\"https://github.com/M-L-P/Yours-UEFI\">Yours UEFI 1</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    不支持：<a href=\"https://github.com/M-L-P/Yours-LegacyBIOS\">Yours LegacyBIOS</a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>（在此感谢上方Github仓库的贡献者！）<br>\n下载最新Release压缩包并解压</p>\n<p><strong>2.安装EFI文件 （以下以支持64位UEFI为例）</strong><br>\n打开DiskGenius，选择SYSTEM_DRV分区并打开<br>\n按照以下步骤复制文件：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n  <p>\n    注意：若想保留Windows原引导，忽略删除EFI\\Boot步骤，并将压缩包中Boot中的Bootx64.efi更名为其他名称，否则Windows容易PIN码失效\n  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yours-UEFI:<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image.png\" /></figure></p>\n<p>Grub2-Fyde:</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\">\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-1.png\" /></figure></p>\n<p><strong>3.调整引导顺序并安装证书</strong><br>\n在DiskGenius中转到”工具=&gt;设置UEFI BIOS启动项”，按照图示新增/修改原Windows引导项</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n  <p>\n    若不保留Windows原引导，请将启动文件替换为\\EFI\\Boot\\Bootx64.efi\n  </p>\n</blockquote><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\">\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/屏幕截图-2025-07-21-191433.png\"  /></figure></p>\n<p>点击保存后，勾选“下次启动时…”，或将该启动项移至最前面，关闭电脑<br>\n在BIOS中暂时禁用安全启动（Secure Boot）<br>\n开机后，出现MokManager页面<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-2.png\" /></figure></p>\n<p>选择OK<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-3.png\"  /></figure></p>\n<p>按下任意键</p>\n<p>选择Enroll key from disk<br>\n接下来找到ENROLL_THIS_KEY_IN_MOKMANAGER.cer，回车，选择Continue=&gt;Yes=&gt;Reboot<br>\n在BIOS中开启安全启动后，即可正常进入引导界面<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-4.png\"  /></figure></p>\n<p>选择FydeOS，回车，之后即可在安全启动下正常使用FydeOS<br>\n之后的引导界面自定义可参考<a href=\"https://github.com/M-L-P/rEFInd-theme-Yours\" target=\"_blank\">rEFInd-theme-Yours </a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Https WordPress建站完全指南","link":"2025/07/29/2025-07-29-https-wordpress"},"next":{"title":"如何在Visual Studio Code中配置C/C++开发环境","link":"2022/04/12/vscode-cpp"},"plink":"http://www.091209.xyz/2025/07/26/2025-07-26-fydeos-uefi/","reading_time":"468 字约 3 分钟"}